  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether adding AF Suppression™ to cardiac
      resynchronization therapy (CRT) improves the prognosis of heart failure patients benefiting
      from cardiac resynchronization therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
